g.text: Example of a COVID19 small submission
This object-set constitutes an example of some objects one would expect in a
small COVID-19 submission that may differ from other types of submissions: an
individual, samples, and the study encompassing all. There are many other
objects one would submit for a full COVID-19 submission: a policy, DAC and
dataset to specify the reusability of the data; experiments and assays
containing the raw data; analyses containing the bioinformatics investigations;
protocols describing each of the procedures performed; and finally a submission
which would be referenced by all objects. This COVID-19 example is
on the COVID-19 example of Phenopackets
